entries.femaleVariant: Close the damn borders, that's what I'd do. Too many bottom-feeders pourin' in from shitholes you've never even heard of!
Lotta folks leaving Night City too. Mostly the ones that can't stand people like you.
I'd say it comes out even.
Well, maybe if we closed the borders, nobody'd try to leave, hm? Ever think about that?
No, but now I know why NC border patrol turned you down.
